# COMAF × PNMS Addendum Units Demo
# Demonstrates all 7 addendum block types (FORCE, POWER, PRESSURE,
# CURVATURE, CHARGE, ENTROPY_UNIT, UNCERTAINTY) from co_af_p3z.md.
# Paper reference: §3 COMAF × PNMS Addendum
# Status: syntax demo (not numerically verified)
ENTITY: AddendumDemo
CYCLE: CPL-1
FRAME: t ∈ [0, 1 WarpTick]
UNITS: Planck

ENTROPY S:
  evolve Boltzmann {
    init: 1e120
    max: 1e121
    scale: 1e9 Plaseconds
  }

STABILITY:
  metric D = exp(-|∇S| · t)

FORCE F_grav: beta * |psi|^2 * R PlaNewtons

POWER P_emit: hbar * c^6 / (M * M) PlaWatts

PRESSURE P_vac: hbar * c / (6 * pi^2) PlaPascals

CURVATURE R_ns: 4.2e42 RicciBits

CHARGE q_eff: alpha * e_p

ENTROPY_UNIT S_tick: k_B

UNCERTAINTY delta_E: hbar / (2 * delta_t)

IF D(t) < 0.01:
  collapse {
    energy: E_jump
    resolution: lambda_p
  }

ON cycle.end:
  S = S / (1 + alpha)
